title: War of the Roses: The Bananas Foster Wedding
description: Lindsay is calling in to make sure marrying her fiance Jack is the right choice.  They are having a very big, extravagant wedding and she wants to be absolutely positive that he's the one before going through with this wedding.  Besides some work stress that's affected their love life, there aren't any red flags, but will doing War of the Roses cause issues?
